INSERT INTO `Faq` VALUES (1,'What is the maximum credit limit I can get?','You can get a credit limit of up to ₹10 thousand. This limit increases as you continue using FatakPay and make timely repayments.','2022-02-11 11:36:46.464215','2022-02-24 05:36:59.259529',0,1,'U',5),(2,'Does FatakPay affect my credit score?','FatakPay is available to all customers, even those without any formal credit history. \r\nIn fact, it is an excellent tool to build or improve your credit score when you make timely payments.','2022-02-11 11:38:25.987046','2022-02-24 05:36:25.823458',0,1,'U',4),(3,'Is there any interest charged by FatakPay?','FatakPay is a 0% interest virtual credit card. There is just a small flat convenience fee for the service.','2022-02-11 11:39:08.867031','2022-02-24 05:35:49.577040',0,1,'U',3),(4,'Why FatakPay?','The more affluent classes have access to easy credit and probably own multiple credit cards, which is an easy/convenient way to make purchases without paying interest. \r\nHowever, a credit card is a reality for only 4% of India\'s population while for the vast majority, credit cards is an inaccessable and aspirational product. \r\nFatakPay has been founded with the intent to bridge this gap and make financial wellness available to all.','2022-02-11 11:39:35.059360','2022-02-24 05:34:47.525126',0,1,'U',2),(5,'What is FatakPay?','FatakPay provides a Virtual Credit Card for all. Its’ available on your Phone and caters to your everyday needs in both online and offline format.  Payments are done seamlessly through UPI/QR codes.	\r\nThe solution provides an Interest free, quick, transparent and a secure way to transact in multilingual format with a Scan Now Pay Later facility and easy repayment options.','2022-02-11 11:40:13.329625','2022-02-24 05:34:03.771023',0,1,'U',1),(6,'Who is eligible to use FatakPay?','FatakPay is for everyone! All you need is a basic smart phone, minimum KYC (Photo Id & Address Proof) and a bank account.','2022-02-17 11:10:16.998419','2022-02-24 07:44:43.400526',0,1,'U',6),(7,'Will FatakPay need the employees\' database to partner with the company?','Yes, we will be collecting information like phone number, KYC, income proof, etc, from the employer, taken on consent from the employee during the onboarding process. \r\nFatakPay will use this information solely for regulatory, underwriting and compliance purposes.','2022-02-19 09:04:08.733706','2022-02-24 06:34:59.864437',0,1,'E',NULL),(8,'How does salary deduction on behalf of employees\' outstanding with FatakPay reflect on the payslip?','The amount deducted to pay any FatakPay outstanding will be mentioned in the \"Other Deductions\" section of the payslip.','2022-02-19 09:04:52.648800','2022-02-24 06:35:37.465692',0,1,'E',NULL),(9,'What happens when an employee resigns or is terminated?','All outstandings over and above the F&F will be recovered by us independently. There will be no liability with the employer.\r\nHowever, the employer is expected to inform Fatakpay of such employee actions.','2022-02-19 09:05:21.700774','2022-02-24 06:36:08.265951',0,1,'E',NULL),(10,'How easy is it to integrate FatakPay into company\'s existing system?','The deployment takes Maximum of 48hrs.\r\nFatakPay is easily integrated with your HRMS/ERP, Payroll, utilising an Application Programming Interface (API). It requires very minimal involvement from the employers\' side.','2022-02-19 09:05:44.685197','2022-02-24 06:36:54.519283',0,1,'E',NULL),(11,'Does FatakPay interfere with the existing loans / employee advances offered to the employees?','No. Fatakpay provides additional support to employees to facilitate managing their cashflows from one payday to the next. \r\nIt also offers an excellent tool that takes care of out of pocket expenses of employees on behalf of the employer. This enables employers to better manage their working capital and employees to better manage their daily cashflow.','2022-02-19 09:06:20.419371','2022-02-24 06:37:44.162618',0,1,'E',NULL);
